# Deprecated Cursor Rules File for nodots-backgammon-ai

This `.cursorrules` file has been superseded by the consolidated rule system located at the workspace root under `.cursor/`.

All nodots-backgammon sub-packages, including **ai**, now automatically inherit shared rules (core, development, coding) from that consolidated configuration.

If you need AI-specific rules in the future, add them via `customRules` in `.cursor/config.json` and regenerate.
